      "x": 620,
      "y": 500,
      "width": 340.40972900390625,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "💡 Prerequisites:\n   • Docker + Docker Compose\n   • NVIDIA GPU + drivers\n   • nvidia-container-toolkit\n   • .env sets COMPOSE_HTTP_TIMEOUT=300\n\n   Verify GPU: nvidia-smi",
