      "type": "text",
      "x": 480,
      "y": 1770,
      "width": 254.296875,
      "height": 143,
      "text": "🐛 Common Issues\n\n• \"Connection refused\"\n  → docker-compose up -d\n\n• \"Model not found\"\n  → docker exec ollama\n    ollama list\n\n• Check GPU in container:\n  docker logs ollama | grep gpu",
